message.body: I broke my phone and had to restore it from a backup from November 3 and now I'm in a weird time warp! Did you say Sunday worked for you for hangouts?
Yeah if you wanna. I'm around all day!
Okay cool! I am meeting a catsitter in the evening but otherwise free. Coffee? Booze drink?
yeah! let’s get an afternoon cocktail somewhere! I’ll think of a place
